fields.name: CollectionInterval
fields.description: The interval in minutes by which metrics will be collected.

fields.name: DetailedStatus
fields.description: The more detailed status of the metrics configuration.

fields.name: DetailedStatusMessage
fields.description: The descriptive message about the current detailed status.

fields.name: DisabledMetrics
fields.description: The list of metrics that are available for the cluster but disabled at the moment.

fields.name: EnabledMetrics
fields.description: The list of metric names that have been chosen to be enabled in addition to the core set of enabled metrics.

fields.name: ProvisioningState
fields.description: The provisioning state of the metrics configuration.
